  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00951', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會團體工作方法的出現，下列敘述何者正確？', '["社會團體工作早期只是團體活動，比社會個案工作更早被認定為社會工作的方法", "社會團體工作方法剛形成的階段，是被用來達成休閒、社會行動、教育和個人成長的目標", "社會團體工作與「俱樂部工作」、「團體調適」完全不同", "社會團體工作的進行過程中，初期強調團體規範，所以民主過程和解決社會問題是被忽略的"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 25, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00952', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '有關社會團體工作中「會心團體」（encountergroup）的敘述，下列何者錯誤？', '["用來促進人際溝通，增進自我了解的團體經驗", "用來使團體成員獲得較佳的自我了解", "用來交心的坦誠團體", "用來達成社會學習所組成的團體"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 26, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00953', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者不是哈佛德（Hartford）所提出的團體主要控制力？', '["團體成員的特質", "團體組織與領導等團體結構", "團體強制力", "團體價值與規範等團體文化"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 27, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('elementary-64311456-moex-00954', 'elementary-64311456', 'elementary-64311456-moex-110-6989845d', 'sub-elementary-64311456-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列那一項為社區工作的主要目標？', '["促進居民參與解決自己的問題，改善生活素質", "改變社區的權力結構分配", "協助社區營利", "推動社區轉型為企業經營模式"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:31:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "afc9a1379873", "answer_pdf_sha1": "36be20ddb9c2", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110010", "c": "502", "s": "0304", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "社會工作大意", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年公務人員初等考試", "original_question_number": 28, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "elementary", "civil_category": "社會行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
